'''NGC 299''' 是[[杜鹃座|杜鹃座]]的一個[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]。該星團位於[[小麦哲伦星系|小麦哲伦星系]]內部，距離地球將近20萬光年<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://astronomynow.com/2016/10/17/hubble-reveals-ngc-299-within-the-small-magellanic-cloud/ |title=Hubble reveals NGC 299 within the Small Magellanic Cloud |accessdate=2016-11-10 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110173114/https://astronomynow.com/2016/10/17/hubble-reveals-ngc-299-within-the-small-magellanic-cloud/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於1834年8月12日由[[約翰·赫歇爾|約翰·赫歇爾]]發現<ref>{{cite web|title=New General Catalog Objects: NGC 250 - 299|url=http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc2a.htm#299|publisher=Cseligman|accessdate=October 18, 2016|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929062322/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc2a.htm#299|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

天文學家分析NGC 299的[[光學重力透鏡實驗|OGLE-III]]測光觀測資料，結果在這個年輕疏散星團內未發現低光變幅度的脈動變星，與其他小麥哲倫星系內的年輕疏散星團不同<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://arxiv.org/abs/1302.6943 |title=Photometric Analysis of Variable Stars in NGC 299 |accessdate=2016-11-10 |archive-date=2016-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110173003/https://arxiv.org/abs/1302.6943 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

